stairdancer
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a sneak thief who specialises in stealing from multistorey buildings.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also earlier dwelling dancer
